# Ability Name		Unique Key						SORTKEY			Category of Ability		Type													Description																																																																																																																			Source, Long Desc.						Source, Short Desc.	Source Page
Improved Evasion		KEY:Waverider Mount ~ Improved Evasion	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.WaveriderMountClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:If the waverider's mount is subjected to an attack that normally allows a Reflex saving throw for half damage, it takes no damage if it makes a successful saving throw and half damage even if the saving throw fails.																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:SS																																																										
Share Spells		KEY:Waverider Mount ~ Share Spells	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.WaveriderMountClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	DESC:At the waverider's option, she may have any spell that she casts on herself (if she is a spellcaster) also affect her mount. This also applies to spell-like abilities. The mount must be within 5 feet. If the spell or spell-like ability has a duration other than instantaneous, the spell stops affecting the mount if it moves farther than 5 feet away and will not affect the mount again even if the mount returns to the waverider before the duration expires. Additionally, the waverider may cast a spell or use a spell-like ability with a target of 'You' on her mount instead of on herself. The waverider and her mount can even share spells that normally do not affect creatures of the mount's type (magical beast).	SOURCEPAGE:SS																																																																																																																																													
Empathic Link		KEY:Waverider Mount ~ Empathic Link		SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.WaveriderMountClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:The waverider has an empathic link with her mount out to a distance of 1 mile. The waverider cannot see through the mount's eyes, but the two can communicate telepathically. Even intelligent mounts see the world differently from their riders, so misunderstandings are always possible.	SOURCEPAGE:SS																																																																																																																																												
Share Saving Throws		KEY:Waverider Mount ~ Share Saving Throws	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.WaveriderMountClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	DESC:The mount uses its own base saves or the waverider's, whichever is higher.	SOURCEPAGE:SS																																																																																																																																													
Fast Movement		KEY:Waverider Mount ~ Fast Movement	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.WaveriderMountClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:The mount's swim speed increases by 5 feet if Small, and by 10 feet if Medium-size or larger.	SOURCEPAGE:SS																																																																																																																																													
Spell Resistance		KEY:Waverider Mount ~ Spell Resistance	SORTKEY:Class_master	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.WaveriderMountClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:The mount gains spell resistance equal to the waverider's class level + 5. To affect the mount with a spell, a spellcaster must make a level check (1d20 + caster level) at least equal to the mount's spell resistance.	SOURCEPAGE:SS																																																																																																																																													
																																																																																																																																																				
