Loom	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:GhostBruteTemplateTrait.GhostBruteAttack.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A ghost brute can make itself more intimidating by exaggerating its natural size. It can appear up to two sizes larger than normal for 10 minutes each day, which need not be continuous. This enlargement is illusory; the creature's attack bonus and Armor Class remain unchanged. However, the ghost brute gains a +4 circumstance bonus on Bluff and Intimidate checks while enlarged.	KEY:Ghost Brute ~ Loom																											SOURCEPAGE:SS																																																																																																																				
